div.p:
The captains receive from $480 to $400; the lieutenants from $320 to
                            $240; brigadiers, $200 to $190; sub-brigadiers from $180 to $170;
                            overseers or préposés, sailors, &c., &c., $160 to 150;
                            storekeepers, $200 to $180.

3d. It takes only young men into service, and thus secures to the state
                            the benefit of their service during the best years of their lives;
                            and,
